  Locus:
    Page: 420
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Self-Realization
---
When we have realized God in all His fullness and perfection, then we have
no difficulties and no obstacles in life. We adjust our life according to
the conditions and circumstances in which God places us. We have no reason
to grumble, complain or feel unhappy at anytime.
